  <brief_title>Uroxatral in Men With Benign Prostate Hypertrophy (BPH) and Erectile Dysfunction (ED)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective, Open Label, Study to Assess the Efficacy of Alfuzosin 10 mg Tablet Once a Day in Male Subjects Suffering From Benign Prostate Hypertrophy Associated Lower Urinary Tract Symptoms and Erectile Dysfunction</official_title>
  <sponsors>
